<div class=3D"pr-0 pr-lg-5">
<h3>How to Manually Calculate a Time Interval</h3>
<p>Manual calculations are time-consuming and prone to errors, so we recomm=
end avoiding them when possible. Still, there may be occasions where you ne=
ed to manually calculate a <a href=3D"https://www.splashlearn.com/math-voca=
