<div class=3D"theAnswer">
<ul>
<li>There are 168 hours in a week.</li>
<li>There are 720 hours in a month with 30 days.</li>
<li>There are 744 hours in a month with 31 days.</li>
<li>There are 8,760 hours in a standard year.</li>
</ul>
<p>The month of February has 672 hours in a standard year. During a <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leap_year">leap year</a>, February is 696=
